@startuml GoDoxy Flow
actor User
participant "main()" as CLI
participant "File System" as FS
participant "Lexical Parser" as Parser
participant "Metadata Extractor" as Meta
participant "Markdown/HTML Generator" as Generator
participant "Search Index Generator" as Search

User -> CLI : Run GoDoxy (Source Path, Output Path)
CLI -> FS : Scan for .h Files
FS --> CLI : List of Header Files

loop For each Header File
    CLI -> FS : Read File Content
    FS --> CLI : Raw C++ String
    CLI -> Parser : Tokenize Content
    Parser -> Parser : Identify Unreal Macros\n(UCLASS, UFUNCTION, etc.)
    Parser --> CLI : List of Identified Tokens & Tags
    
    CLI -> Meta : Extract Signatures & Comments
    Meta --> CLI : Structured Metadata\n(Params, Returns, Meta tags)
end

CLI -> CLI : Build Dependency/Cross-Ref Map

loop For each Class/Struct/Enum
    CLI -> Generator : Render Documentation (Templates)
    Generator -> FS : Write .md / .html Files
end

CLI -> Search : Generate Search Index
Search -> FS : Save search_index.json

CLI --> User : Documentation successfully generated!
@enduml
